{"tid":2457862,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「連燈力」基金 呂布軍第二十次股東大會，小勝U後退兵，保持連勝不敗之姿！","createTime":"2021-03-23T03:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T08:37:54.000Z","uid":149018,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"21cf4af5fae66e12003eeeadb661647e2e071c89","tid":2457862,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第十九次軍議結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zd4ytnk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZd4ytnk.png&h=6797bf3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aPOhfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aPOhfF.png&h=57811e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jOZ8nk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jOZ8nk.png&h=8918a351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4czWtk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4czWtk.png&h=bce85a29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"green\">933.49</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">6.65</span>%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第二十波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，穩健投資，為燒賣舖進發。<br />\n<br />\n一軍為短期戰線Daytrade陷陣營，二軍為一周長期戰線赤兔部隊。<br />\n請諸將及軍師團註明兩軍進軍方向提議<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次軍議操作為ALL IN制， 收集此帖巴打軍師將領主流意見<br />\n2. 收集軍師兵士們之股票後<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">聽天由命</span></span>買入。<br />\n3. 一軍買入時間預計為盤前<span class=\"red\">16:00</span>。<br />\n4. 一軍陷陣營不買入妹十世股，二軍赤兔隊不選擇QQQ<br />\n5. 一軍陷陣營賣出時機分為&darr;<br />\na. 到達預計賣出時間為盤前21:00、盤後07:45或開市緊急調動<br />\nb. 增幅到達7%將立即設下5%止蝕位保存勝仗<br />\nc. 10%止賺及止蝕位，若為QQQ 上下限改為3%。<br />\n6. 若陷陣營該次結算資金增長5% 隨機選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<br />\n7. 呂布將保留最終決定權<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UR2XWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR2XWx.jpg&h=9062ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1</a><br />\n第十九次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2456189/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2456189/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">呂布曰：感謝上蒼讓奉先於萬紅之中覓得亮路。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呂布昨夜機智退兵，武力100 智力<span class=\"green\">84</span>操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jAc4z4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjAc4z4D.jpg&h=935167ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a95604e323855c1cdcc700ef1aa59a38ff5e0891","tid":2457862,"uid":134094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"GME<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ff46fedac8b5e4bb020876e9dc8ed2a3a5a380","tid":2457862,"uid":149018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a95604e323855c1cdcc700ef1aa59a38ff5e0891","tid":2457862,"uid":134094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"GME<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:46:44.000Z","msg":"神棍GME"},{"pid":"833269520dd80f333d2ba6f54ca71b3a08e891d5","tid":2457862,"uid":18085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"tkat!!!"},{"pid":"1c66d61e1df86e3e2675fdb3125cc21f611ffffb","tid":2457862,"uid":393265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"AAL"},{"pid":"3ec442118dd3b34779bbb42f094f1a4edcc51172","tid":2457862,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3ff46fedac8b5e4bb020876e9dc8ed2a3a5a380","tid":2457862,"uid":149018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a95604e323855c1cdcc700ef1aa59a38ff5e0891","tid":2457862,"uid":134094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"GME<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime"